Package ua.java.conferences.controller.actions.implementation.moderator

This is moderator package. It contains all moderators actions implementations. ChangeTopicAction - to change reports topic CreateEventAction - to create new conference CreateReportAction - to create new report DeleteEventAction - to delete conference DeleteReportAction - to delete report EditEventAction - to edit conference EventsToPdfAction - to get event's list in pdf SearchEventAction - to find event by title SetOrRemoveSpeakerAction - to set or remove speaker for report SetVisitorsAction - to set visitors number for conference ViewEventsAction - to get event's list ViewReportAction - to view report
